money and the woman is a 1940 british crime film directed by james m. cain and written by james m. cain . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , william frawley , george barbier , william demarest , george barbier , william demarest , george barbier , william demarest , george barbier , william demarest , george barbier , william demarest , william frawley , george barbier , william frawley , george siegmann , william demarest , and jack hoxie . the film was released on june 2 , 1940 , by 20th century fox .